        "action": "Fund schools to support pupils with SPD ",
        "additional_details": "Because not many people know about it and people are suffering with it and don\u2019t know how to deal or cope with it.",
        "background": "The Government should provide funding to schools to help them support children with Sensory Processing Disorder (SPD). Children with SPD need to be able to go to a safe space in the school which has ear defenders and sensory toys, to calm down when things get too much.",
